lead_paragraph: U.S. gymnast Gabby Douglas turned in a near flawless performance at Sunday's Olympic qualifying event, gaining the third highest score of any gymnast, but because of Olympic rules she will not be going to the all around final.

headline.print_headline: Gymnastics: Despite Flawless Day, U.S.'s Douglas Won't Defend London Gold
